Germany. Likewise, OROS hydromorphone was dominant in the treatment of chronic 
severe malignant pain when compared with ER oxycodone in both Germany and 
Denmark and when compared with bid hydromorphone in all markets where 
hydromorphone was marketed.
CONCLUSIONS: This model demonstrates the cost effectiveness of OROS 
hydromorphone relative to other strong oral opioids in the treatment of chronic 
